15 (III) MOVING A PRESCRIPTION DRUG TO A MORE RESTRICTIVE
16 TIER IF THE ENTITY USES A FORMULARY WITH TIERS; AND
17 (IV) REMOVING A PRESCRIPTION DRUG FROM A FORMULARY,
18 UNLESS:
19 1. THE U.S. FOOD AND DRUG ADMINISTRATION HAS
